Package: MG2
Title: Magic Glasses 2: Epidemiological Analysis of DHIS2 Health Data
Version: 0.1.8
Date: 2026-06-14
Authors@R:
    person("John", "Painter", , "painter.ja@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-1750-8391"))
Description: An interactive Shiny application and set of R functions for
    exploring, assessing, and analyzing routine health data from DHIS2
    information systems. Supports data quality assessment, outlier detection,
    reporting bias analysis, and time-series trend evaluation. Functions can
    also be used independently in standalone scripts and notebooks.
